<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1887-03-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1887-03-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="613" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d613">
                    <head>No. 613.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Curry</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi></head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1887-03-10"><hi rend="italic">March</hi> 10,
                            1887</date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Mr. Curry informs the Department that the Government of Spain is willing to
                        extend the duration of the agreement of October 27, until the 30th of June
                        next.</p>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>